00:00:15.920 --> 00:00:21.440
Clive Nicoli and Elsa Kast are a genetic&nbsp;
engineer couple working for a company named&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:21.440 --> 00:00:28.240
Nucleic Exchange Research and Development (NERD).&nbsp;
Their primary job at the company is to conduct&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:34.080
