create hybrid creatures with unique qualities.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:34.080 --> 00:00:39.280
The company’s aim is to use the unique compounds&nbsp;
found in the hybrid’s body to create medicines&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:39.280 --> 00:00:44.400
that can treat most of the diseases in the world.&nbsp;
At the beginning of the movie, we see Clive and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:50.240
