Everyone watches in fascination as Fred and Ginger&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:56.560 --> 00:01:01.280
meet for the first time and create a ball-like&nbsp;
shape with their tongues to greet each other. 
&nbsp;

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:07.920
Later, Clive and Elsa are in a meeting with the&nbsp;
CEO of the company, Joan Chorot. Joan is delighted&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:12.480
with the result of their experiment and wants to&nbsp;
start extracting genetic materials that will help&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:12.480 --> 00:01:18.000
them create medicines immediately. The couple&nbsp;
