00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:33.680
Joan wants to focus on the existing hybrids&nbsp;
at the moment. Elsa insists that if they don’t&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:39.360
do it first, someone else will. But the CEO is&nbsp;
adamant about her decision. The couple comes out&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:39.360 --> 00:01:44.800
